      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MAJESTIC ETHICS (3) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing seventh (19.90) in a Grade 5 at this track. Rates on top in this line up. BAREFOOT CHAOS (1) was strongly fancied last time and hit the ground running with a slick early split, giving a sight but could manage only second (17.59) at Taree Super Track over 300m. Comes through a solid form race last start. Will give a great sight again. ZABDON CREAM BUN (2) produced a moderate run last time when seventh at this track over 350m behind Last Love (20.51) in a Restricted WIN. Must be included in calculations. LUCY BURROW (4) looks an each-way chance.",
